 be black and what it meant to be radical in Britain.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aBlack peoplezGreat BritainxHistoryy20th century. 0aBlack peoplezGreat BritainxPolitics and governmenty20th century. 0aBlackszGreat BritainxHistoryy20th century. 0aBlackszGreat BritainxPolitics and governmenty20th century. 0aRadicalismzGreat BritainxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Great Britain / 20th Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311066767740uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052096720540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520967205423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520967205/original  a978-3-11-066767-7  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles